Section2.Para:
The genotype of each isolate was identified by SmaI-digested PFGE analysis, and the results were visually interpreted as previously described [21, 22]. The MLST types of 16 CA- and HA-MRSA isolates were identified using the method described by Enright [23] and by reference to MLST databases (
                    http://saureus.mlst.net

                  ).
